      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that people disagree, but u r a macroeconomist... surely there's a more objective way to look at it. like, if the debt gets too high, isn't that just objectively bad for the economy in the long run? isn't debt reduction the more \"responsible\" path regardless of politics?",
