      "content": "but that's basically just saying we should keep spending to grow the economy. isn't that a bit of a circular argument? if you just keep adding to the debt to fund \"stimulus,\" you never actually solve the underlying problem of fiscal insolvency. isn't it more \"balanced\" to admit that cutting spending is a necessary evil to prevent a total crash later?",
